<h2>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</h2>

<h4>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</h4>

<h5><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></h5>

<h6>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</h6>
<h6>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</h6>
